Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.60,Main,Ex,0,0,0,,And there you have it. \N Well... goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:16.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Last week, on Saturday, my boyfriend of \N six and a half years broke up with me by text.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:20.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The next day, Sunday, I stepped in gum \N while wearing my favorite shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,On Monday, \N I was late for a vital presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,On Tuesday, \N a colleague{kouhai} I was close to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wednesday, \N I trimmed my eyebrows all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:28.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thursday, the curry I spent \N three hours making tasted terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Friday, I messed up \N a vital presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And on Sunday, \N I stepped in gum again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I am now here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:45.81,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Daddy! Look at the Camome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.94,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,You can see the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.60,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:13.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The Pokémon Resort... \N I’m really here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:16.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Fushigidane!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:18.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:22.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You’re the new employee, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:25.02,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,The boat ride must have \N been exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh! Are you part of the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ll be working here starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,My name is Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:39.27,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Haru-san, welcome to \N the Pokémon Resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:41.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:10.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The Pokémon really do \N come here as guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.73,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,See you later, Metagross!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:24.31,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:27.65,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,people and Pokémon \N can have fun separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:28.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,We also have Pokémon on staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,And sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s this? A Wooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:37.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Much like this one, \N some wild Pokémon settle down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:42.06,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Around here, \N our motto is “Pokémon first.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,And our job...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,...is to look after these Pokémon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,In other words, \N you’ll be the Pokémon concierge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Concierge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.35,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:02.44,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Koratta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:06.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,H—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:07.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:11.06,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Okay, that’s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:14.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Ootachi, no fighting here, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.60,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Let’s get you somewhere \N a little more spacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.31,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,It’s also a concierge’s job \N to keep our guests safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:33.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Now then, I know you’ve just arrived \N but I’ve got a very important job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:41.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’d like for you \N to spend the day as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:45.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But I’m staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:49.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Well, then... Make yourself at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Could it be... I’m being tested?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.90,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,I think I’ll have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.52,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, I wanna try those lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.60,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Heya! There ya are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.52,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s my first day of work today—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.10,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Yeah! You’re Haru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.90,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Name’s Tyler. Sanitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,And fitness lessons, just for fun. \N Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.85,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Staff Pokémon. Guess you could \N call ‘em my right-hand crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:48.40,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,They can be real pranksters, \N so you’d better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,So, I’ll be—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Yeah! You’ll be doing it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.23,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Good thing you did warm-ups, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Come back any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:32.19,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I also teach swimming, \N yoga, and wakeboarding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.35,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,You’re taking a trip \N ‘round the resort, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.77,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Go ahead and use those kick scooters!{They're not kick scooters, but that is what he says (and when they come up next episode they just say scooters) and (far as we're aware) it doesn't seem like the term is used interchangeably in Japanese in ways it isn't in English. - Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.10,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Hurry up! I’m leaving without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.52,Main,Human being,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Comment: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ve never been on \N one of these before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,So much for seniority. \N He didn’t teach me {\i1}anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} a Pokémon paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.27,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,All right! Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,My name is Haru, \N and I started working here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.27,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,I’m Alisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.52,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,I work here part-time every summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, the pleasure is all—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mizugoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wait, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.23,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.60,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Just started following me around one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Did you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You’re so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.44,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,It does that sometimes, \N even when it’s happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.52,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,So... What’s up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Well, today is my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And I have no idea \N what I’m supposed to be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.73,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Weren’t you supposed to \N spend the day as a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I mean... That’s what \N I was told to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Whoa! The pressure is intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Am I going to get lectured?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.69,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The old “meet me \N behind the gym” cliché?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that’ll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,In here Pokémon can \N get all stylish too, right?{in the much like people could sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:03.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Trimming makes up the basics, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.52,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Getting something like \N a new hairdo or a matching outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.73,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,...seems to make Pokémon \N pretty happy, too.{wari to}{Again in the "much like it would with people" sense.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:13.19,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Well, this kind of thing’s{read: making customers look nice n' stylish} \N what the job is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,This kind of thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.73,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Hey! Lunch is almost ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? We get free meals here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.19,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Tyler’s cooking. It’s pretty good.{wari to}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Blue skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Blue sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A tasty lunch amid the sea breeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The Pokémon Resort is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:57.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ve needed this...{Literally "All the time I never got to have time like this"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Um... Is it true that \N I can get a massage here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:29.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.56,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Please come right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:33.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What? From you, Watanabe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:39.44,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m so skilled I can make \N any Pokémon fall asleep with a touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yeah, but maybe... I don’t know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.35,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:58.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Um... I met some of the other staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,They’re all pretty interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yeah. They’re definitely unique...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:10.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Both of them had Pokémon with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.44,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,As a matter of course, you become friends \N and then they just stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:20.44,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m sure there’s a Pokémon \N you’ll get along with, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I can’t wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.31,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Ma’am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:42.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Okay, that was {\i1}not{\i0} good! \N I got way too relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And I fell asleep \N in front of my supervisor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I {\i1}need{\i0} to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.90,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Uh... Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.02,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,So, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:21.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What did you think? \N Could you give me your impressions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:30.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right! I built a report on my activities yesterday \N and drafted a personal work plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:34.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The Pokémon Resort prides itself \N in its luxurious atmosph—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:39.40,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,As much as I appreciate \N that you compiled all that data,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,that was not quite \N what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I-I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I just compiled it in a way that would \N work for me... I’ll give it another...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Say, Haru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,How did yesterday go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:59.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,When you ask me “how”...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to answer?!{This is what Japanese work culture does to you}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:29.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Haru-san? \N Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No... It was just... funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What’s funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The Pokémon here are doing \N what they want and having fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:44.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,and when I saw that, I started feeling \N like I was stupid to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:47.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ve just had nothing but \N bad experiences as of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:50.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And it made me wonder, \N what even {\i1}is{\i0} my life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:54.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But I’ve been having so much fun that \N all those gloomy feelings just faded away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh... I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be my job, \N and here I talk about it like a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,No, that is exactly \N what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:03.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,As long as you understand that, \N you’ll do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:14.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,This here is proof \N that you are a concierge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,The only rule is \N you need to wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:21.06,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Aside from that, you can do \N whatever you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:21.81,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:24.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,So then, what exactly is my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.56,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Well, I have one request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:34.44,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Find one Pokémon—any will do—\Nand before the sun sets,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:38.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I want you to make that Pokémon \N feel the same way that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A crazy hard mission right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I acted like I understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:55.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,but I have no idea what was \N “just fine” about what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Koduck?
Comment: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:20.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
