Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:13.73,ED,Place to be of you,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}Your job is just to have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:19.52,ED,Place to be of you,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}You kept your nose to the grindstone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:23.85,ED,Place to be of you,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Just spinning your gears each day
